punto-n60-nset100.dat: a 3D particle data in "punto" format
(http://sourceforge.net/projects/punto)

punto2xyz.awk: a script to change punto format to xyz format

rxyz.tcl: vmd script to vizulize (adjust change radius of the atoms)

Usage:
awk -f punto2xyz.awk punto-n60-nset100.dat > punto.xyz
vmd -e rxyz.tcl -xyz punto.xyz
